22
00:01:55,587 --> 00:01:57,868
Niente di grave, la solita vitamina di influenza.

23
00:01:58,468 --> 00:01:59,409
Ah, bene.

24
00:01:59,450 --> 00:02:00,891
Un macello, allora.

25
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:03,951
